001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.BiochemicalReaction;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.DeltaG;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.KPrime;
006import org.biopax.paxtools.util.BPCollections;
007
008import java.util.Set;
009
010
011public class BiochemicalReactionImpl extends ConversionImpl
012        implements BiochemicalReaction
013{
014// ------------------------------ FIELDS ------------------------------
015
016        private Set<Float> deltaS;
017        private Set<KPrime> kEQ;
018        private Set<Float> deltaH;
019        private Set<DeltaG> deltaG;
020        private Set<String> eCNumber;
021
022// --------------------------- CONSTRUCTORS ---------------------------
023
024// --------------------- ACCESORS and MUTATORS---------------------
025
026        public BiochemicalReactionImpl()
027        {
028                this.deltaG = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
029                this.deltaH = BPCollections.I.createSet();
030                this.deltaS = BPCollections.I.createSet();
031                this.eCNumber = BPCollections.I.createSet();
032                this.kEQ = BPCollections.I.createSafeSet();
033        }
034
035// ------------------------ INTERFACE METHODS ------------------------
036
037
038// --------------------- Interface BioPAXElement ---------------------
039
040        public Class<? extends BiochemicalReaction> getModelInterface()
041        {
042                return BiochemicalReaction.class;
043        }
044
045// --------------------- Interface BiochemicalReaction ---------------------
046
047        public Set<DeltaG> getDeltaG()
048        {
049                return deltaG;
050        }
051
052        protected void setDeltaG(Set<DeltaG> deltaG)
053        {
054                this.deltaG = deltaG;
055        }
056
057        public void addDeltaG(DeltaG deltaG)
058        {
059                if(deltaG != null)
060                        this.deltaG.add(deltaG);
061        }
062
063        public void removeDeltaG(DeltaG deltaG)
064        {
065                if(deltaG != null) 
066                        this.deltaG.remove(deltaG);
067        }
068
069        public Set<Float> getDeltaH()
070        {
071                return deltaH;
072        }
073
074        public void addDeltaH(float deltaH)
075        {
076                this.deltaH.add(deltaH);
077        }
078
079        public void removeDeltaH(float deltaH)
080        {
081                this.deltaH.remove(deltaH);
082        }
083
084        public Set<Float> getDeltaS()
085        {
086                return deltaS;
087        }
088
089        public void addDeltaS(float deltaS)
090        {
091                this.deltaS.add(deltaS);
092        }
093
094        public void removeDeltaS(float deltaS)
095        {
096                this.deltaS.remove(new Float(deltaS));
097        }
098
099        public Set<String> getECNumber()
100        {
101                return eCNumber;
102        }
103
104        public void addECNumber(String eCNumber)
105        {
106                this.eCNumber.add(eCNumber);
107        }
108
109        public void removeECNumber(String eCNumber)
110        {
111                this.eCNumber.remove(eCNumber);
112        }
113
114        public Set<KPrime> getKEQ()
115        {
116                return kEQ;
117        }
118
119        public void addKEQ(KPrime kEQ)
120        {
121                this.kEQ.add(kEQ);
122        }
123
124        public void removeKEQ(KPrime kEQ)
125        {
126                this.kEQ.remove(kEQ);
127        }
128
129}
